| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6733 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e3ca4824-5fe1-59f5-9d4e-fca8e9ca5126"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
